## Live2D Cubism SDK License  

### 1. Commercial Use Requirements  
- **If a company's sales in the most recent fiscal year reach or exceed 10 million JPY**, it must obtain **a publishing license for the Cubism SDK** (Publishing License Agreement).  
  - For details, see: [Cubism SDK Release License](https://www.live2d.com/en/sdk/license/)  

### 2. Component Licenses  
The official Live2D license descriptions are as follows:  
- **Live2D Cubism Core**: Subject to the **Live2D Proprietary Software License**.  
- **Live2D Cubism Samples**: Subject to the **Live2D Open Software License**.  
- **Live2D Cubism Framework**: Subject to the **Live2D Open Software License**.  

